Parameters:
target - The Target to aim at. Used to find network table keys
axis - The axis (x or y) to look for
timeout - How long (seconds) until the PIDCommand times out
continuous - If continuous, it never ends!!! MUAHAHAHA!!!!
p - P value for PID controller
i - I value for PID controller
d - D value for PID controller
tolerance - the tolerance for the PID controller
maxOutput - the absolute value of the maximum output
